General.Name: Shanghai Kaytune Industrial Co.Ltd
General.Description: Shanghai Kaytune Industrial Co.,Ltd provides e-commerce and customer relationship management services to enterprises. It also offers customer management, brand marketing, visual design, store operation, logistics distribution, system development, and member management services, as well as operates customer service center. The company was formerly known as Shanghai Kaiyi Industrial Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Shanghai Kaytune Industrial Co.,Ltd in October 2016. Shanghai Kaytune Industrial Co.,Ltd was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Shanghai, China.
